834~109,4,Required when the Custodial Parent contact information is provided to the sponsor\046 If not required by this implementation guide\044 do not send\046
834~109,5,1\046 When the communication number represents a telephone number in the United States and other countries using the North American Dialing Plan \040for voice\044 data\044 fax\044 etc\046\041\044 the communication number always includes the area code and phone number using the format AAABBBCCCC\044 where AAA is the area code\044 BBB is the telephone number prefix\044 and CCCC is the telephone number \040e\046g\046 \040534\041224\0452525 would be represented as 5342242525\041\046
