834~43~4~22~1~0,0,Use this code when a member changes from one\r\nPlan to a different Plan\046 This is not intended to identify changes to a Plan\046
834~43~4~25~1~0,0,Use this code when a change has been made to the primary elements that identify a member\046 Such primary elements include the following\058 first name\044 last name\044 Social Security Number\044 date of birth\044 and employee identification number\046
